headline: Capital One Financial (COF) Emphasizes AI and Strategic Growth at Morgan Stanley Conference
summary: Capital One Financial Corporation (NYSE:COF) is one of the best Goldman Sachs bank stocks. On June 10, at the Morgan Stanley US Financials Conference 2025, Capital One CEO Rich Fairbank discussed the Discover merger as a transformative opportunity to expand Capital One’s scale in credit cards, strengthen its position in payments, and accelerate its progress […]

headline: Fintech sector: Capital One co-founder explains what's next
summary: Fintech surged in 2021, has since fallen back from these highs, and is now showing signs of stabilizing. Nigel Morris, co-founder of Capital One (COF) and co-founder and managing partner of QED Investors, joins Catalysts with Madison Mills to share his outlook for fintech and what he believes will drive growth for the sector. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Catalysts here.
